VYOU AWAKE CONFUSED,|NO MEMORY OF HOW|YOU GOT HERE...|BUT A NOTE SITS|IN YOUR POCKET...3"HOLD UP, STRANGER...|YOU'RE NOT FROM|AROUND HERE."7"THIS PLACE MAY NOT|LOOK LIKE MUCH,|BUT IT'S OUR HOME."X"OUR FAMILIES LIVED HERE|BEFORE THE BOMBS,|AND WE'VE FOUGHT EVERY DAY|TO KEEP IT ALIVE."'"NOW HARLAN VALE|WANTS TO TAKE IT ALL."X"HE'S GOT RAIDERS, MACHINES,|AND ENOUGH FIREPOWER|TO WIPE EVERY SETTLEMENT|OFF THE MAP."""ORDINARY WEAPONS|WON'T STOP HIM.">"BUT THERE IS ONE WEAPON|THAT CAN."| |"THEY CALL IT BIG IRON."/"A REVOLVER BUILT TO FIRE|SIX SPECIAL BULLETS."e"EACH ROUND WAS MADE TO|TEAR THROUGH VALE'S ARMOR|AND DESTROY PART OF THE|MACHINE KEEPING HIM ALIVE."O"BUT THE BULLETS WERE|SCATTERED ACROSS|THE WASTELAND."| |"YOU'LL NEED ALL SIX.";"ONE BULLET FOR EVERY|PIECE OF VALE THAT|NEEDS DESTROYING."K"MISS EVEN ONCE, AND HE|MAY SURVIVE LONG ENOUGH|TO FINISH WHAT HE STARTED."4"PLEASE, STRANGER...|FIND THE SIX|BIG IRON BULLETS."'"HELP US SAVE THIS PLACE|WE CALL HOME."="AND WHEN YOU FINALLY|STAND FACE-TO-FACE|WITH HARLAN VALE...""MAKE EVERY SHOT COUNT."*A DOG WHIMPERS*.*CHUCK*|HIS COLLAR READS.| |ARE YOU... MY DOG?ź*AFFIRMING BARK*